title: The Settlers - Rise of Cultures (English modded)
description:
The Settlers - Rise of Cultures was originally released only in German as Die Siedler - Aufbruch der Kulturen

I have done my best in converting this game to English. Some of it is rough translation.

Extract the 7zip file, install PhysX in support folder. Must use version provided the game would not launch for me with newer version. Launch game with SADK.exe in bin folder.

Tested on Windows 7 64bit, works great!
